---
// Narrative arc: LLM War Over → Stock Memory Too Late → It Adapts → The Edge
// Full dark theme to continue hero energy
---

<!-- Wrapper: stays dark throughout -->
<div style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #050510 0%, #0a0f1a 30%, #0c1220 60%, #0a0f1a 100%); color: #E2E8F0;">

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- Section 1: The LLM War Is Over                                 -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="py-28 md:py-36 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Ambient glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,158,11,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(30%, -50%);"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[4px] mb-6" style="color: #F59E0B; opacity: 0.7;">The shift</p>
        <h2 class="font-logo text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight" style="color: #F8FAFC;">
          The LLM war is over.<br/>
          <span style="color: #64748B;">Memory is what's left.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6" style="color: #94A3B8;">
          GPT-4o, Claude, Llama, Gemini &mdash; converging capability, converging price. Every team gets the same models. Switching costs are zero.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed" style="color: #94A3B8;">
          The differentiator isn't which model you pick. It's what your agent <strong style="color: #F8FAFC;">remembers between conversations</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Visual: Commodity vs Edge -->
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl p-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15);">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #64748B;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #CBD5E1;">Reasoning</span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15); color: #64748B;">commodity</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl p-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15);">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #64748B;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M8 9l3 3-3 3m5 0h3M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #CBD5E1;">Generation</span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15); color: #64748B;">commodity</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl p-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15);">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #64748B;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #CBD5E1;">Tool calling</span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(100,116,139,0.15); color: #64748B;">commodity</span>
        </div>

        <!-- The edge -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl p-4 relative" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.06); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-xl pointer-events-none" style="box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(245,158,11,0.08);"></div>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15);">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" style="color: #F59E0B;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-semibold" style="color: #F8FAFC;">Memory</span>
          </div>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full font-semibold" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.15); color: #F59E0B;">your edge</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- Section 2: Stock Memory Is Already Too Late                    -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="py-28 md:py-36 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent);"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[4px] mb-6" style="color: #F87171; opacity: 0.7;">The problem</p>
    <h2 class="font-logo text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight" style="color: #F8FAFC;">
      Stock memory is already<br/>
      <span style="color: #F87171;">too late.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-14 max-w-2xl" style="color: #94A3B8;">
      Every vector database gives you one strategy: similarity search. One knob: top-k. No evals, no domain profiling, no self-improvement. The gap is non-linear.
    </p>

    <!-- Side-by-side comparison -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Stock -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 relative" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(248,113,113,0.1); color: #F87171;">generic</span>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background: rgba(100,116,139,0.1);">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #475569;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm mb-5" style="color: #64748B;">Standard RAG / Vector DB</p>
        <div class="space-y-3.5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #64748B;">
            <span style="color: #334155;">&#10005;</span> Similarity search only
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #64748B;">
            <span style="color: #334155;">&#10005;</span> No temporal reasoning
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #64748B;">
            <span style="color: #334155;">&#10005;</span> No causal chains
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #64748B;">
            <span style="color: #334155;">&#10005;</span> No domain tuning
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #64748B;">
            <span style="color: #334155;">&#10005;</span> No contradiction detection
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #64748B;">
            <span style="color: #334155;">&#10005;</span> Retrieval: static forever
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 pt-5 font-mono text-xs" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); color: #334155;">
          cosine &gt; 0.7 LIMIT k &mdash; every query, forever
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- HEBBS -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 relative" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.15); box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(245,158,11,0.05);">
        <div class="absolute top-4 right-4">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.12); color: #F59E0B;">tuned for you</span>
        </div>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1);">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" style="color: #F59E0B;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <p class="font-mono text-sm mb-5" style="color: #F59E0B;">HEBBS</p>
        <div class="space-y-3.5">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #CBD5E1;">
            <span style="color: #F59E0B;">&#10003;</span> 4 strategies: similarity + temporal + causal + analogical
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #CBD5E1;">
            <span style="color: #67E8F9;">&#10003;</span> "What happened in order?" &mdash; temporal
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #CBD5E1;">
            <span style="color: #34D399;">&#10003;</span> "What caused this?" &mdash; causal chains
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #CBD5E1;">
            <span style="color: #A78BFA;">&#10003;</span> Domain-profiled, eval-tuned, self-improving
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #CBD5E1;">
            <span style="color: #F87171;">&#10003;</span> Contradictions surface automatically
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm" style="color: #CBD5E1;">
            <span style="color: #FBBF24;">&#10003;</span> Retrieval: compounds every tune cycle
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-8 pt-5 font-mono text-xs" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.1); color: #92400E;">
          strategy-selected &middot; weight-tuned &middot; domain-aware
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- Section 3: It Adapts to You                                    -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="py-28 md:py-36 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent);"></div>
  <!-- Ambient glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] rounded-full pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(103,232,249,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-30%, -50%);"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[4px] mb-6" style="color: #67E8F9; opacity: 0.7;">Self-tuning</p>
    <h2 class="font-logo text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8 leading-tight text-center" style="color: #F8FAFC;">
      It adapts to you.<br/>
      <span style="color: #64748B;">Not the other way around.</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-16 max-w-2xl text-center mx-auto" style="color: #94A3B8;">
      HEBBS profiles your domain, generates evals, measures baseline, diagnoses failures, tunes parameters, and compiles learned rules. Switch your LLM &mdash; the memory adapts.
    </p>

    <!-- Tuning loop: connected pipeline -->
    <div class="relative">
      <!-- Connecting line -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-[52px] left-[12.5%] right-[12.5%] h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, #F59E0B, #67E8F9, #34D399, #A78BFA);opacity:0.2;"></div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 text-center relative" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.04); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.12);">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 relative" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(245,158,11,0.1);">
            <span class="font-mono text-lg font-bold" style="color: #F59E0B;">01</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2" style="color: #F59E0B;">Profile</p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94A3B8;">Classify domain, map query patterns</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 text-center" style="background: rgba(103,232,249,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(103,232,249,0.1);">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4" style="background: rgba(103,232,249,0.1); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(103,232,249,0.08);">
            <span class="font-mono text-lg font-bold" style="color: #67E8F9;">02</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2" style="color: #67E8F9;">Evaluate</p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94A3B8;">Domain evals, real keywords, strict match</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 text-center" style="background: rgba(52,211,153,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(52,211,153,0.1);">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4" style="background: rgba(52,211,153,0.1); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(52,211,153,0.08);">
            <span class="font-mono text-lg font-bold" style="color: #34D399;">03</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2" style="color: #34D399;">Tune</p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94A3B8;">Fix k, strategy, weights, cue expansion</p>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 text-center" style="background: rgba(167,139,250,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(167,139,250,0.1);">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4" style="background: rgba(167,139,250,0.1); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(167,139,250,0.08);">
            <span class="font-mono text-lg font-bold" style="color: #A78BFA;">04</span>
          </div>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-2" style="color: #A78BFA;">Compile</p>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #94A3B8;">Rules file loads before every conversation</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Repeat indicator -->
      <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full px-6 py-2.5" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" style="color: #F59E0B;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
          <span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: #94A3B8;">Repeat when content changes, models change, or retrieval misses</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- Section 4: The Edge (75% → 94%)                                -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="py-28 md:py-36 relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent);"></div>
  <!-- Big ambient glow behind the numbers -->
  <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-[700px] h-[700px] rounded-full pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,211,153,0.06) 0%, rgba(245,158,11,0.03) 40%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-50%, -50%);"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 text-center">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[4px] mb-6" style="color: #34D399; opacity: 0.7;">The result</p>
    <h2 class="font-logo text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-3" style="color: #F8FAFC;">
      Same model. Same data.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl mb-20" style="color: #64748B;">Different memory engine.</p>

    <!-- Dramatic before/after -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="font-mono font-bold leading-none mb-3" style="font-size: clamp(64px, 12vw, 120px); color: rgba(248,113,113,0.6);" data-counter="75">75<span style="font-size: 0.5em;">%</span></div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: #475569;">stock retrieval</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 md:w-20 md:h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(245,158,11,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10" style="color: #F59E0B;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: #F59E0B;">tuned</span>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="font-mono font-bold leading-none mb-3" style="font-size: clamp(64px, 12vw, 120px); color: #34D399;" data-counter="94">94<span style="font-size: 0.5em;">%</span></div>
        <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest" style="color: #475569;">HEBBS retrieval</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Context bar -->
    <div class="inline-flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 rounded-2xl px-8 py-5" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background: #F59E0B;"></div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: #94A3B8;">GPT-4o + OpenAI embeddings</span>
      </div>
      <span style="color: #1E293B;">|</span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background: #67E8F9;"></div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: #94A3B8;">Strict keyword recall</span>
      </div>
      <span style="color: #1E293B;">|</span>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style="background: #34D399;"></div>
        <span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color: #94A3B8;">Agent-tuned in 60 seconds</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-10 text-sm" style="color: #475569;">
      +19 percentage points. Not by changing the LLM. By tuning how the agent retrieves.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

</div>
